bpf: Enable bpf_{g,s}etsockopt in BPF_CGROUP_UDP{4,6}_SENDMSG

Can be used to query/modify socket state for unconnected UDP sendmsg.
Those hooks run as BPF_CGROUP_RUN_SA_PROG_LOCK and operate on
a locked socket.

